examples.en: I like to delve into old books looking for forgotten history.
Before he was appointed, the committee delved into his past record.
He tried to delve inside his memory for clues about what had happened.
A delve into which I can put my thumb.
A poem in which a medieval knight encounters a mysterious beauty in a darkened delve.
He quickly learns that every delve of his spade in the earth means money.
